<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>以色列新闻RSS</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Thu, 08 Feb 2024 18:08:38 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>战争中的以色列：您需要了解的内容 – 第 125 天</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-08/ty-article/.highlight/israel-at-war-what-you-need-to-know-day-125/0000018d-89d1-d5e7-ad8d-ebf1fac20000</link><description>布林肯表示，哈马斯对停火提议的回应“显然不可能”，但美国认为“这为达成协议创造了空间” ■ 哈马斯高级官员表示，内塔尼亚胡对哈马斯的答复表明总理打算在该地区寻求冲突 ■ 几名以色列人周四，一名真主党指挥官在黎巴嫩的火箭弹和导弹袭击中受伤</description><pubDate>Thu, 08 Feb 2024 17:49:55 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-08/ty-article/.highlight/israel-at-war-what-you-need-to-know-day-125/0000018d-89d1-d5e7-ad8d-ebf1fac20000</guid></item><item><title>当以色列艺术家不再是以色列艺术家时</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/life/2024-02-08/ty-article/.premium/this-week-in-culture-when-an-israeli-artist-is-not-an-israeli-artist/0000018d-892a-d9cc-a5cd-fdba9e700000</link><description>在本周的以色列文化综述中：艺术家兼电影制片人雅埃尔·巴塔纳 (Yael Bartana) 将代表德国参加今年的威尼斯双年展，海法取消了为两位失去亲人的父亲（一位是以色列人，另一位是巴勒斯坦人）举办的一本书的活动，特拉维夫博物馆仍在展出展览与赎罪日战争的斗争</description><pubDate>Thu, 08 Feb 2024 17:25:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/life/2024-02-08/ty-article/.premium/this-week-in-culture-when-an-israeli-artist-is-not-an-israeli-artist/0000018d-892a-d9cc-a5cd-fdba9e700000</guid></item><item><title>英国首相誓言打击亲巴勒斯坦集会上的“反犹太主义”和“暴力恐吓”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-08/ty-article/britains-pm-vows-to-crack-down-on-antisemitism-at-pro-palestine-rallies/0000018d-897b-d443-a19f-fdfbabef0000</link><description>英国首相谴责伦敦抗议活动中表现出的“美化恐怖主义”，并发誓在英国反犹太主义率不断上升的情况下，警方将“阻止人们遮住脸来隐瞒身份”</description><pubDate>Thu, 08 Feb 2024 17:17:16 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-08/ty-article/britains-pm-vows-to-crack-down-on-antisemitism-at-pro-palestine-rallies/0000018d-897b-d443-a19f-fdfbabef0000</guid></item><item><title>纽约一家德鲁兹餐厅的墙上挂着一面以色列国旗。这时候麻烦就开始了</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-02-08/ty-article-magazine/.premium/a-druze-restaurant-in-ny-hung-an-israeli-flag-on-the-wall-thats-when-the-trouble-started/0000018d-880f-d0de-af8d-8c3fd87c0000</link><description>在曼哈顿的加扎拉餐厅，老板加扎拉哈拉比自豪地认为自己是以色列人，所用的橄榄油、香草和香料都是从“家乡”带来的。 10月7日之后的尖酸刻薄、破碎的玻璃和“自由巴勒斯坦”的涂鸦让她震惊，但她无意退缩</description><pubDate>Thu, 08 Feb 2024 16:28:37 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-02-08/ty-article-magazine/.premium/a-druze-restaurant-in-ny-hung-an-israeli-flag-on-the-wall-thats-when-the-trouble-started/0000018d-880f-d0de-af8d-8c3fd87c0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列撤离人员所在的酒店报告了多起性暴力和家庭暴力案件</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-08/ty-article/.premium/several-cases-of-sexual-and-domestic-violence-reported-at-hotels-housing-israeli-evacuees/0000018d-891d-d443-a19f-fd9d8bf20000</link><description>据警方称，已立案 116 起单独档案，其中包括针对未成年人和妇女的性侵犯案件。由于持续的战争，加沙和黎巴嫩边境地区共有约20万人流离失所</description><pubDate>Thu, 08 Feb 2024 15:56:55 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-08/ty-article/.premium/several-cases-of-sexual-and-domestic-violence-reported-at-hotels-housing-israeli-evacuees/0000018d-891d-d443-a19f-fd9d8bf20000</guid></item><item><title>随着加沙的生活和家园被摧毁，其高等教育也被摧毁</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2024-02-08/ty-article-opinion/.premium/as-gazas-lives-and-homes-are-destroyed-so-is-its-higher-education/0000018d-8906-d970-a5ed-8976424f0000</link><description>加沙高等教育的破坏不是“附带损害”，而是以色列摧毁物质和精神基础设施政策的一部分</description><pubDate>Thu, 08 Feb 2024 15:40:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2024-02-08/ty-article-opinion/.premium/as-gazas-lives-and-homes-are-destroyed-so-is-its-higher-education/0000018d-8906-d970-a5ed-8976424f0000</guid></item><item><title>10 月 7 日袭击中丧生的以色列男子的家人告知加沙的尸体</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-08/ty-article/.premium/family-of-israeli-man-killed-in-oct-7-attack-informed-body-held-in-gaza/0000018d-892e-d5e7-ad8d-ebaecd4b0000</link><description>贝埃里的梅尼·戈达尔和他的妻子在哈马斯袭击基布兹期间被杀。迄今为止，他的家人仍不知道他遗体的下落</description><pubDate>Thu, 08 Feb 2024 15:35:03 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-08/ty-article/.premium/family-of-israeli-man-killed-in-oct-7-attack-informed-body-held-in-gaza/0000018d-892e-d5e7-ad8d-ebaecd4b0000</guid></item><item><title>特拉维夫居民因在公寓内刺伤妇女而被起诉</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-08/ty-article/.premium/tel-aviv-resident-indicted-in-fatal-stabbing-of-woman-in-her-apartment/0000018d-887e-d061-abff-afff1b570000</link><description>犯罪嫌疑人是 33 岁的丹尼尔·马尔戈辛 (Daniel Margoshin)，他在夜间闯入受害人家中，刺伤她超过 31 刀。他放火烧毁了公寓和她的尸体，然后逃到耶路撒冷，在那里他试图袭击试图逮捕他的警察，结果被枪杀。</description><pubDate>Thu, 08 Feb 2024 15:26:35 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-08/ty-article/.premium/tel-aviv-resident-indicted-in-fatal-stabbing-of-woman-in-her-apartment/0000018d-887e-d061-abff-afff1b570000</guid></item><item><title>阿根廷总统在访问被哈马斯蹂躏的以色列基布兹时将10月7日描述为“21世纪纳粹主义”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-08/ty-article/.premium/argentine-president-describes-oct-7-as-21st-century-nazism-at-israeli-kibbutz/0000018d-891b-d061-abff-affbcf6c0000</link><description>极右翼总统米莱表示，“当我们听到 10 月 7 日所使用的方法时，这让我们想起了大屠杀的暴行”。他对犹太教着迷，并表示有兴趣皈依犹太教。</description><pubDate>Thu, 08 Feb 2024 15:06:08 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-08/ty-article/.premium/argentine-president-describes-oct-7-as-21st-century-nazism-at-israeli-kibbutz/0000018d-891b-d061-abff-affbcf6c0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列关于战争的艺术展不是“战争展览”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-08/ty-article-magazine/.premium/an-israeli-art-exhibit-on-the-war-that-isnt-a-war-exhibition/0000018d-839d-d636-adef-cfff28230000</link><description>压抑的紧张感和克制的恐怖：特拉维夫英加画廊的展览受到加沙战争的影响，但以一种广泛的、存在主义的方式</description><pubDate>Thu, 08 Feb 2024 14:12:47 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-08/ty-article-magazine/.premium/an-israeli-art-exhibit-on-the-war-that-isnt-a-war-exhibition/0000018d-839d-d636-adef-cfff28230000</guid></item><item><title>加沙人逃离家园。他们无处可归| “这令人震惊”：170 万巴勒斯坦人逃离了以色列对加沙的轰炸。他们的大部分房屋都被损坏或摧毁</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/security-aviation/2024-02-08/ty-article-static-ext/.premium/gazans-fled-their-homes-they-have-nowhere-to-return-to/0000018d-73f0-d4f1-a18d-f7f071190002</link><description>卫星揭示了加沙地带遭受的巨大破坏。以色列国防军的行动所创造的新现实将在数年内影响整个地区。这就是它的样子</description><pubDate>Thu, 08 Feb 2024 13:59:13 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/security-aviation/2024-02-08/ty-article-static-ext/.premium/gazans-fled-their-homes-they-have-nowhere-to-return-to/0000018d-73f0-d4f1-a18d-f7f071190002</guid></item><item><title>“我不得不离开以色列。 10月7日之后，我就不能再碰画笔了。”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/life/2024-02-08/ty-article-magazine/.premium/i-had-to-leave-israel-after-oct-7-i-wasnt-capable-of-touching-a-brush/0000018d-8888-dbf5-ab9d-cb8878a40000</link><description>10 月 7 日大屠杀发生几天后，以色列德鲁兹艺术家法特玛·沙南 (Fatma Shanan) 离开以色列前往欧洲。她解释了为什么她觉得有必要逃避阿拉伯以色列人不断要求谴责哈马斯袭击的要求</description><pubDate>Thu, 08 Feb 2024 13:36:02 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/life/2024-02-08/ty-article-magazine/.premium/i-had-to-leave-israel-after-oct-7-i-wasnt-capable-of-touching-a-brush/0000018d-8888-dbf5-ab9d-cb8878a40000</guid></item><item><title>“我们将消灭犹太人”：希特勒的“孙子”和穆夫提在新的埃及电影中相遇</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-08/ty-article/.premium/we-will-destroy-the-jews-grandsons-of-hitler-and-the-mufti-meet-in-new-egyptian-movie/0000018d-8869-d0de-af8d-8c79fdc70000</link><description>在《一个世纪又六年》的这场奇幻邂逅中，两人发誓要实现祖父的愿望，消灭犹太人和以色列。这部电影获奖了，但阿拉伯世界的反应却很冷淡</description><pubDate>Thu, 08 Feb 2024 13:24:57 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-08/ty-article/.premium/we-will-destroy-the-jews-grandsons-of-hitler-and-the-mufti-meet-in-new-egyptian-movie/0000018d-8869-d0de-af8d-8c79fdc70000</guid></item><item><title>以色列警方在没有合法理由的情况下没收反政府抗议者的装备</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-08/ty-article/.premium/israel-police-confiscate-anti-govt-protesters-equipment-without-legal-cause/0000018d-8816-d0de-af8d-8c36354a0000</link><description>在最近几周针对内塔尼亚胡政府的抗议活动中，尽管抗议者保持允许的噪音水平，但警方还是没收了扩音器、鼓和扬声器系统，导致冲突和拘留</description><pubDate>Thu, 08 Feb 2024 12:23:38 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-08/ty-article/.premium/israel-police-confiscate-anti-govt-protesters-equipment-without-legal-cause/0000018d-8816-d0de-af8d-8c36354a0000</guid></item><item><title>“1948 年的创伤已被唤醒”：策展人希望将艺术带回以色列南部</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-08/ty-article-magazine/.premium/bringing-art-back-to-israels-obliterated-south-the-trauma-of-1948-has-been-reawakened/0000018d-83e2-d636-adef-cfee1e2d0000</link><description>基布兹 Yad Mordechai 可能被描述为一个带有基布兹的纪念场所，而不是相反。自10月7日起，基布兹的美术馆已关闭。它的馆长现在正在寻找复兴它的方法</description><pubDate>Thu, 08 Feb 2024 11:23:49 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-08/ty-article-magazine/.premium/bringing-art-back-to-israels-obliterated-south-the-trauma-of-1948-has-been-reawakened/0000018d-83e2-d636-adef-cfee1e2d0000</guid></item><item><title>美国与以色列矿业巨头丹·格特勒的斗争确凿无疑？</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-08/ty-article/.premium/a-smoking-gun-in-u-s-fight-against-israeli-mining-magnate-gertler/0000018d-7eac-d636-adef-7eee1fed0000</link><description>根据 TheMarker 获得的记录，以色列商人 Dan Gertler 显然透露了他如何规避美国因涉嫌在刚果行贿而实施的制裁，并隐瞒了一座价值 15 亿美元的铜钴矿。他的律师：“无意义的主张”</description><pubDate>Thu, 08 Feb 2024 10:38:31 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-08/ty-article/.premium/a-smoking-gun-in-u-s-fight-against-israeli-mining-magnate-gertler/0000018d-7eac-d636-adef-7eee1fed0000</guid></item><item><title>OPSEC失败：以色列军队在加沙的阵地在网上可见</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/security-aviation/2024-02-08/ty-article/.premium/opsec-failure-israeli-army-forces-positions-in-gaza-are-visible-online/0000018d-8813-d424-abad-9b5b70490000</link><description>在犯了无数错误之后，以色列国防军发布了明确的指导方针，以防止敏感信息泄露。但这些并没有得到执行，以色列士兵在加沙作战时不断暴露自己的行动和立场</description><pubDate>Thu, 08 Feb 2024 10:29:37 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/security-aviation/2024-02-08/ty-article/.premium/opsec-failure-israeli-army-forces-positions-in-gaza-are-visible-online/0000018d-8813-d424-abad-9b5b70490000</guid></item><item><title>以色列北部发现超罕见的白色彩虹</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/travel/parks-nature/2024-02-08/ty-article/.premium/ultra-rare-white-rainbow-spotted-in-northern-israel/0000018d-8825-d424-abad-9b7d8a920000</link><description>白色彩虹不是在雨中而是在雾中观察到。就像彩虹一样，要看到彩虹，你需要在太阳身后看着雾气</description><pubDate>Thu, 08 Feb 2024 10:22:28 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/travel/parks-nature/2024-02-08/ty-article/.premium/ultra-rare-white-rainbow-spotted-in-northern-israel/0000018d-8825-d424-abad-9b7d8a920000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡克制地与哈马斯作战直到“全面胜利”是一个幻想</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-08/ty-article/.premium/netanyahus-refrain-of-fighting-hamas-until-total-victory-is-a-fantasy/0000018d-87eb-df76-a1fd-cffb8ba20000</link><description>本杰明·内塔尼亚胡认为自己是温斯顿·丘吉尔，不断谈论与哈马斯的战争中的“全面胜利”。他拒绝接受的是，他实际上是二战角色扮演中的绥靖者内维尔·张伯伦。以色列公众对他的信任已从根本上被打破</description><pubDate>Thu, 08 Feb 2024 10:21:32 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-08/ty-article/.premium/netanyahus-refrain-of-fighting-hamas-until-total-victory-is-a-fantasy/0000018d-87eb-df76-a1fd-cffb8ba20000</guid></item><item><title>尽管内塔尼亚胡蔑视哈马斯的提议，但他为以色列谈判敞开了大门</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-08/ty-article/.premium/despite-netanyahus-scorn-for-hamas-proposal-he-leaves-the-door-open-for-negotiations/0000018d-87bf-df76-a1fd-cfff7c7a0000</link><description>政治消息人士认为，总理的蔑视实际上可能为继续谈判奠定了基础。美国国务卿布林肯还表示，尽管哈马斯的回应存在问题，但它“为达成协议创造了空间”</description><pubDate>Thu, 08 Feb 2024 10:12:28 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-08/ty-article/.premium/despite-netanyahus-scorn-for-hamas-proposal-he-leaves-the-door-open-for-negotiations/0000018d-87bf-df76-a1fd-cfff7c7a0000</guid></item></channel></rss>